nl_command: you can leave after College Hall is observed otherwise stay at Butcher
ltl: U butcher college_hall

nl_command: stay on Memorial Tower until you reach Stouffer Commons
ltl: U memorial_tower stouffer_commons

nl_command: stay on Wilson until you reach Rodney
ltl: U wilson rodney

nl_command: once James G. Kaskey Memorial Park is seen feel free to leave 1920 Commons otherwise stay at 1920 Commons
ltl: U 1920_commons james_g._kaskey_memorial_park

nl_command: once Fitler is seen feel free to leave Stouffer College House otherwise stay at Stouffer College House
ltl: U stouffer_college_house fitler

nl_command: you must keep going on 1920 Commons until you get to CHOP Parking Garage
ltl: U 1920_commons chop_parking_garage

nl_command: you must keep going on Foerderer until you get to Warwick
ltl: U foerderer warwick

nl_command: do not leave New York Alumni before Chestnut is seen
ltl: U new_york_alumni chestnut

nl_command: do not leave Coxe before Baldwin is seen
ltl: U coxe baldwin

nl_command: immediately after you visit CHOP Parking Garage you must visit Leonard and Madlyn Abramson Pediatric Research Center
ltl: G i chop_parking_garage X leonard_and_madlyn_abramson_pediatric_research_center

nl_command: immediately after you visit Warwick you must visit Brooks
ltl: G i warwick X brooks

nl_command: right after you visit Perelman Center for Advanced Medicine you must go to USPS Postbox
ltl: G i perelman_center_for_advanced_medicine X usps_postbox

nl_command: right after you visit Children's Hospital of Philadelphia you must go to Children's Seashore House of CHOP
ltl: G i children's_hospital_of_philadelphia X children's_seashore_house_of_chop

nl_command: you need to head to Baldwin immediately whenever you visit Coxe
ltl: G i coxe X baldwin

nl_command: you need to head to Warwick immediately whenever you visit Stouffer College House
ltl: G i stouffer_college_house X warwick

nl_command: do not go to anywhere but Perelman Center for Advanced Medicine once you visit Rodney
ltl: G i rodney X perelman_center_for_advanced_medicine

nl_command: do not go to anywhere but Coxe once you visit Foerderer
ltl: G i foerderer X coxe

nl_command: if you visit Warwick make your way right to Children's Seashore House of CHOP right after that
ltl: G i warwick X children's_seashore_house_of_chop

nl_command: if you visit Wawa make your way right to McKean right after that
ltl: G i wawa X mckean
